        <h1>Mathematics for Machine Learning</h1>
        
          <p>Companion webpage to the book "Mathematics for Machine Learning". Copyright 2020 by Marc Peter Deisenroth, A. Aldo Faisal, and Cheng Soon Ong. Published by Cambridge University Press.</p>
        
